# Folio — SECRETS only, for local `wrangler dev` + the Cloudflare deploy prompt.
# Copy to apps/web/.dev.vars (git-ignored) and fill in.
#
# Non-secret config (FOLIO_AUTH_MODE, FOLIO_OWNER_ID, FOLIO_FAVICON,
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST) lives in wrangler.jsonc `vars`
# with sensible defaults — keep it OUT of here so the Cloudflare deploy setup
# page doesn't prompt for the same key twice, and so no secret is pre-filled.

# REQUIRED — gates the /admin editor in token mode. Set a long random string
# (e.g. `openssl rand -hex 32`). Left empty, /admin stays locked.
FOLIO_ADMIN_TOKEN=""

# OPTIONAL — PostHog analytics. Publishable project key, inlined at build time.
# Leave empty to run without analytics.
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=""

# OPTIONAL — full click→signup→revenue attribution via Almanac. Set BOTH to
# enable; leave empty to run standalone on the PostHog path.
ALMANAC_URL=""
ALMANAC_API_KEY=""
